class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822761025bfc40f827d6c1450f6b90074deaaa6f","tid":406802,"uid":54076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T20:29:58.000Z","msg":"Copenhagen 同 Iceland（環島）必去<br />\n有時間可以去埋Oslo Bergen <br />\nStockholm太西歐覺得無乜特色<br />\n而Helsinki 就真係太悶<br />\n個人覺得瑞典芬蘭可以不去"},{"pid":"9e8ecaed92f9d2cac5f2d7a710eebe31cf5e8d8b","tid":406802,"uid":74102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T00:57:10.000Z","msg":"出年三月我都會去北歐，會去冰島, Tromso, Abisko, Kiruna, Stockholm, Oslo同Bergen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3878221a0af5fe64de2403413796cf2a13720b","tid":406802,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:15:37.000Z","msg":"多謝各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野食方面如何"},{"pid":"2230734f92310f380790c478e4bb5faaa69b9846","tid":406802,"uid":18430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野食方面如何</blockquote><br />\n比晒suggestion 你就自己搵喇 廢架你？"},{"pid":"45c3c63ba4c8898a8dc13886c3a727f266e0dce9","tid":406802,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T07:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野食方面如何</blockquote><br />\n大城市咩國家食物都有<br />\n中西日美都有"},{"pid":"07b491f9e93220d1a4ab32baf035093845c48c61","tid":406802,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:41:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多謝各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野食方面如何</blockquote><br />\n大城市咩國家食物都有<br />\n中西日美都有</blockquote><br />\n中日一定好貴，不過我喺日本住日餐可免"}]}